Package at.tugraz.ist.ase.csp2choco.antlr

Interface CSP2ChocoListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
CSP2ChocoBaseListener, CSP2ChocoTranslator
public interface CSP2ChocoListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CSP2ChocoParser.
